{"tid":288340,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"windows 10其實係咪有問題/唔兼容ssd","createTime":"2017-06-18T06:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T07:31:06.000Z","uid":43653,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de5b95e421a79e3641306aa27009ba5fe6ea91b2","tid":288340,"uid":43653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T06:20:28.000Z","msg":"我部電腦2011年砌 當時裝左windows7<br />\n之後上個月 我OS可能clash左開唔到機<br />\n但入面有資料要用 冇得直接洗機/砌過部<br />\n所以我諗住買新既正版windows10+裝入新買既ssd<br />\n然後開機+back up番d資料 再洗機當新機用<br />\n<br />\n但當我裝完win10之後 當時版本係1607, 我一開完登入畫面 部電腦就會自己黑屏/死mon+紅點<br />\n我能夠做既 只係不停reboot/用安全模式開<br />\n<br />\n我back up完所有野+洗機後重裝幾次(uefi/唔用uefi既方法都裝過) 都仲係有同樣既問題, 之後我上windows download 1703版本黎整usb手指再重裝 都係有同樣問題<br />\n最後 我用安全模式update Nvidia既driver先可以正常開到機一兩次 但隔一陣就再死過機<br />\n<br />\n其實係我硬件太舊同win10唔兼容定我顯卡driver有問題？<br />\n如果我宜家e塊底板 又頂唔頂到新既顯卡e.g. GeForce GTX 1050 Ti ??<br />\n<br />\n底板: ASUS P8Z77-M Pro<br />\nCPU: i7-2600k @3.40GHz<br />\n顯卡: Nvidia GeForce GTX 560Ti<br />\nSSD: PHY PHANTOM SSD 120GB (新買)<br />\nRAM: 8GB DDR3"},{"pid":"1b9d9c2dc8c7ba19f94d9517553fb644e0b98bba","tid":288340,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T17:54:55.000Z","msg":"你唔去問 microsoft ?<br />\n顯你老母卡"},{"pid":"471a33550edd8863fce85ee81546cf629b295364","tid":288340,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T17:58:41.000Z","msg":"咁堆ultrabook死哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5297cce199061bc75828aa668a9bd105bc2000dd","tid":288340,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T23:50:25.000Z","msg":"比返個腦人啦"},{"pid":"2ab9a06aade0702699d89e06ee4d423bc1d0a020","tid":288340,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T00:02:43.000Z","msg":"我都有煩似嘅疑問，唔知windows 10用ssd 係咪要set 啲咩野<b